===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|la|fulminātus}}, past participle of {{m|la|fulminō||lighten, hurl or strike with lightning}}, from {{m|la|fulmen||lightning which strikes and sets on fire, thunderbolt}}, from earlier {{m|la|*fulgmen}}, {{m|la|*fulgimen}}, from {{m|la|fulgeō}}, {{m|la|fulgō||flash, lighten}}. {{doublet|en|fulmine}}. More at {{l|en|fulgent}}.

